METAR String:
Plain Text
HAAB 101100Z 09006KT 9999 FEW025 23/03 Q1025 NOSIG =


 Breakdown & Meaning
HAAB
 Airport Code
HAAB = Addis Ababa Bole International Airport (Ethiopia)
101100Z
 Date & Time (UTC/Zulu time)
10 = Month ka 10th din
1100Z = 11:00 UTC time
 Agar IST me dekhe:
UTC + 5:30 = 16:30 IST (4:30 PM)
09006KT
 Wind (Hawa ki direction & speed)
090 = Hawa East (Purab) se aa rahi hai
06KT = Speed 6 knots (~11 km/h)
 Matlab: Halki hawa, purab se
9999
 Visibility (Dekhne ki duri)
9999 = 10 km ya usse zyada visibility
 Matlab: Bilkul clear visibility
FEW025
 Clouds (Badal)
FEW = Thode se badal (1–2 oktas)
025 = 2500 feet altitude par
 Matlab: Thode badal, kaafi clear sky
23/03
 Temperature / Dew Point
Temperature = 23°C
Dew Point = 3°C
 Matlab: Weather dry hai, humidity kaafi kam
Q1025
 Atmospheric Pressure
1025 hPa
 Matlab: High pressure → stable & acha weather
NOSIG
 No Significant Change
Aane wale 2 ghante me weather me koi khaas change nahi

