Relative Humidity --> Temprature - dew point

QNH (Pressure --> Station level pressure reduced to sea level pressure)

1013.2hpa--> Standard Pascal pressure

less than 1013.2hpa --> Low pressure --> Bad weather --> strong and wind

more than 1013.2 hpa--> high pressure--> good and stable condition


